'''貝爾斯河'''（Beles River）是[[埃塞俄比亞|埃塞俄比亞]]西部的河流，是[[青尼羅河|青尼羅河]]的支流。

貝爾斯河從發源地向西南方流至其匯流點，而流域面積約14,200平方公里。<ref>[http://www-wds.worldbank.org/external/default/WDSContentServer/WDSP/IB/2008/05/09/000334955_20080509032052/Rendered/PDF/434000PAD0P09617372B01off0use0only1.pdf "Tana & Beles Integrated Water Resources Development: Project Appraisal Document (PAD), Vol.1"] {{Wayback|url=http://www-wds.worldbank.org/external/default/WDSContentServer/WDSP/IB/2008/05/09/000334955_20080509032052/Rendered/PDF/434000PAD0P09617372B01off0use0only1.pdf |date=20160304193613 }}, World Bank, 2 May 2008 (accessed 5 May 2009)</ref>

